There are a limited number of options remaining to leave Estonia via commercial routes, but these are reducing and are subject to change at short notice.
Please check with Tallinn Airport, Tel: +372 605 8888 for available routes and planned departures for passenger information.
The Finnish Government have announced the suspension of passenger travel on ferries from Tallinn to Helsinki with effect from 11 April 2020. The recommendation will be in force until 13 May 2020. Please contact Port of Tallinn, Tel: (+372) 631 8550 for passenger information and the Finnish Border Guard website for more information if you are planning to leave Estonia via Finland.
The Estonian Ministry of Foreign Affairs publishes regular updates on travel options and regulations on their website.
